{"tid":860904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有遊行人士舉起「 美軍未來我邀請 美軍來了我帶路」口號","createTime":"2018-10-13T16:38:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T23:45:42.000Z","uid":5195,"like":93,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6d512520b709f2c4e730d94c4f2370b4d8d2c613","tid":860904,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T16:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/blogger/2016/08/%E5%B0%8F%E9%AF%8A01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fblogger%2F2016%2F08%2F%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%25AF%258A01.png&h=0601da6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/blogger/2016/08/%E5%B0%8F%E9%AF%8A02.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fblogger%2F2016%2F08%2F%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%25AF%258A02.png&h=888edd89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線昨發起遊行，抗議港府政治篩選參選人，民陣估計有1300人參與遊行，警方則指高峰期有760參加， 參加情況未算太踴躍。<br />\n<br />\n 據網上新聞報道，話參加遊行者有數人高舉港英旗及美國國旗， 要求外國政府介入跟進事件。<br />\n<br />\n有朋友傳來一兩張圖片，應該是昨日拍的照片，有遊行人士打起「 美軍未來我邀請 美軍來了我帶路」的口號，都相當得人驚。橫額上書「 促請美國嚴正介入選舉政治審查事件及香港主權前途問題， 帶路光榮，解放東亞」。署名「香港帶路青年團」。<br />\n<br />\n照片又見港獨人士「中出羊子」和持橫額者站在一起。 記得他報名參選立法會新界西直選時，就自稱「美軍帶路羊」， 期後被取消參選資格。<br />\n<br />\n 那些歡迎在校園自由討論港獨的教育界團體，想必十分歡迎「 香港帶路青年團」這些港獨組織，在學校招收會員， 叫學生齊齊立志，為美軍帶路。看完這些東西，小鯊才明白「 數典忘祖」的意思。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/1342887-%E3%80%8C%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E4%BE%86%E4%BA%86%E6%88%91%E5%B8%B6%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F1342887-%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25BB%258D%25E4%25BE%2586%25E4%25BA%2586%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E3%2580%258D&d=4XZylA6XlayF4Sd6DE6TKl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=29af3a33\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/1342887-%E3%80%8C%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E4%BE%86%E4%BA%86%E6%88%91%E5%B8%B6%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%8D</a>"},{"pid":"b11cec4fa8c3a10362d27cfdfae9d09969533254","tid":860904,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T18:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28918001e2e7877c954f895718ff1663d275559","tid":860904,"uid":99205,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T18:57:50.000Z","msg":"屌，仲擺埋pose<br />\n頂隱"},{"pid":"a38d1d2e00931fcfe920c85d569986efd6a85ce9","tid":860904,"uid":65984,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T19:03:31.000Z","msg":"2012「走私武器彈藥罪」被捕判監<br />\n<br />\n2015年11月「洗黑錢」罪名拘捕<br />\n<br />\n佢係咪揸白卡所以次次咁快出得返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01e92106be2e2a6711b2da6c99e0fea36118ef0","tid":860904,"uid":182125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a38d1d2e00931fcfe920c85d569986efd6a85ce9","tid":860904,"uid":65984,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T19:03:31.000Z","msg":"2012「走私武器彈藥罪」被捕判監<br />\n<br />\n2015年11月「洗黑錢」罪名拘捕<br />\n<br />\n佢係咪揸白卡所以次次咁快出得返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T19:10:22.000Z","msg":"難為班後生妹妹仔仲係蚛國坐緊監"},{"pid":"621686b7834849d6eb33dfe4edcd2aba38cc406e","tid":860904,"uid":33352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T19:23:16.000Z","msg":"公主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c63baef945e18c1837dfb4ef20405e1282216a46","tid":860904,"uid":4330,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T19:29:54.000Z","msg":"咩中出羊子呢d柒碌好心收番埋啦<br />\n唔好笑死人"},{"pid":"8c8afedb8bff90eaeae87fb44e54428432e7aba1","tid":860904,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T19:30:08.000Z","msg":"中出小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26f23e486fe4be3450